=== java安装

==== linux(centos-stream9)

.java8
[source, bash]
----
#安装java8
yum install -y java-1.8.0-openjdk java-1.8.0-openjdk-devel java-1.8.0-openjdk-headless

#查看当前java环境
java -version
----


